casebody.data:
Frank Skonieczka and Pearl Utecht, 264 Willett Street, Buffalo, New York, Respondents, v. Elsa James Garvin, 1105 Delaware Avenue, Buffalo, New York, and Elizabeth Armstrong, 526 Ashland Avenue, Buffalo, New York, Appellants.

Judgment and order affirmed, with costs. All concur. (The judgment is for plaintiffs in an automobile negligence action. The order denies a motion for a new trial.)

Present — Lewis, Cunningham, Taylor and Dowling, JJ.
